snippet.title: UNO - Launch Trailer (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
UNO, the iconic card game, is available on Nintendo Switch™! Be the first to empty your hand.

FOUR THEMES
Vary your experience with the Rabbids, Just Dance, Rayman or Winter Themes.

SHARE THE FUN
Play against your friends locally or online and be the first one to empty your hand.

AVAILABLE NOW
